JOHANNESBURG A family of five has been gunned down in Hillbrow, in downtown Johannesburg on Monday.Gauteng police who have launched a manhunt for the suspects said three women and two children were shot at approximately 8pm.Police said the motive for the multiple murders is unknown and are pleading to anyone who might have any information that can lead to the arrest of the suspect or suspects to please contact them. It is alleged that the suspect or suspects entered the residence of the victims and shot all the deceased on their upper bodies, said Captain Mavela Masondo. The motive for this gruesome murder is unknown and police are investigating five cases of murder. eNCA